{"tid":2407846,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【五年的洗禮】 黃台仰磨滅囂張嘗試了解泛民  社運不止改變制度還有思想","createTime":"2021-02-14T11:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T15:23:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1818f1b71328b58c55b654cdf983a946099c3a","tid":2407846,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:23:06.000Z","msg":"【五年的洗禮】<br />\n黃台仰磨滅囂張嘗試了解泛民 <br />\n社運不止改變制度還有思想<br />\nFeb 14, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-ife4u0QrVQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-ife4u0QrVQ&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuVSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=aa40a981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-ife4u0QrVQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n57.7K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n「我很記得2016年在網台的時候，和梁天琦一起討論泛民，當時我們很討厭泛民，講咗很多鬧泛民嘅嘢，其實係幾唔成熟，唔係話泛民唔抵鬧，但如果我嘗試設身處地企喺佢哋嗰個時空，對佢哋有多啲了解，可能批評佢哋嘅語氣上會無咁重。」<br />\n<br />\n曾經說過「寧為玉碎，不作瓦全」的黃台仰，經歷被控暴動、隱身流亡、再到國際游說工作，五年過後，多了一份不慍不火。他形容以前的自己有少少目中無人，今天在待人處事上成熟了很多，順利的話今年五月將獲得德國居留許可，兩年後大學畢業。<br />\n<br />\n人在變，社會都在變。由2016年旺角衝突之後，到2017年離港流亡，他一直都感受到社會對勇武抗爭的隔膜，離開前一刻還被泛民支持者，指責有沒有感到愧疚。但反送中運動爆發後，民眾對激烈行為的同情大很多，雖然和理非不會參與激烈行動，但最起碼不會割席，會視前線為整場運動的一部份。<br />\n<br />\n一串魚蛋引起的騷動，經過五年的洗禮，「光復香港時代革命」的倡議無人不曉，民眾包容和勇不分的抗爭手法、香港人的本土身份認同根深柢固，誰能說清魚蛋革命的成功或失敗？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuVSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=20d9d367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com</a>​"},{"pid":"ec439c9f4ea258258256ae2f650d87516c2f7491","tid":2407846,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NRsGaGu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNRsGaGu.png&h=07165d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iD8jTLBJ8vI&amp;ab_channel=JJHin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiD8jTLBJ8vI%26ab_channel%3DJJHin&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuVSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=797f2ee3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iD8jTLBJ8vI&amp;ab_channel=JJHin</a>"},{"pid":"83c6cefd5e255dd9d90334697c700828b38eeaf4","tid":2407846,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T12:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556019ab842a87bbd443a855b82afdc710ac22d2","tid":2407846,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:19:20.000Z","msg":"唔好呀.....<br />\n咁會好快變泛民之流。"},{"pid":"4af79cea94768e699fb28555520ac288d5b67f6d","tid":2407846,"uid":289157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"說好了的不作瓦全呢"}]}